Deaths in 122 U.S. cities - 1962-2016. 122 Cities Mortality Reporting System.

Sample dataset for examples. Derived from CDC 122 cities dataset.

flugam: compute influenza estimates using Generalized Additive Models from the mgcv package.

fluglm: Generate fitted prediction values with generalized linear model.

flum: General modeling function for Attributable Influenza Mortality
